test_steps: Navigate to the login page
Click on 'Sign in with email'
Enter valid email address and password, and click 'Continue'
Verify that user is authenticated successfully
Verify that user can navigate to other pages within the application
expected_results: User is successfully authenticated and redirected to the dashboard

test_steps: Navigate to the login page
Click on 'Sign in with email'
Enter an empty email address and password, and click 'Continue'
Verify that user is not authenticated
Verify that error message is displayed indicating invalid email address
expected_results: User is not authenticated and remains on the login page
Error message indicating invalid email address is displayed
